cast.overview: A group of survivors take refuge in a shopping mall after the world is taken over by aggressive, flesh-eating zombies.
cast.title: Dawn of the Dead

details.biography: Matt Austin (born Matt Sadowski; 20 April 1978) is a Canadian actor who is known for his role as Green Ranger (later Blue Ranger, then Red Ranger in the "Power Rangers Operation Overdrive" "Once A Ranger" team-up story arc) and Bridge Carson in the American TV series "Power Rangers: S.P.D.". In addition to his acting skills, he is also a writer, musician, and filmmaker.
details.name: Matt Sadowski-Austin
